title: Seiko Prospex SPB143
description: A modern reinterpretation of Seiko's classic dive watch with a robust 200m water resistance, automatic movement, and a sapphire crystal. Sporty yet refined for everyday wear.

title: Casio G-Shock GA-2100-1A
description: Ultra-slim shock-resistant digital-analog G-Shock with carbon core guard structure, world time, and 200m water resistance — built for rugged daily use.

title: Tissot PRX Powermatic 80
description: A sleek 1970s-inspired integrated-bracelet watch with Powermatic 80 automatic movement (80-hour power reserve), refined dial finishing, and versatile style for dress or casual looks.

title: Citizen Eco-Drive Promaster Diver
description: Eco-Drive solar-powered diver with ISO-compliant construction, luminous markers, and a unidirectional bezel — reliable performance without battery changes.

title: Rado Centrix – Modern Elegance Crafted in Time
description: The Rado Centrix embodies contemporary luxury with its sleek design and innovative materials. Renowned for its high-tech ceramic construction, this watch offers exceptional comfort, scratch resistance.
